com.googlecode.n_orm.storeapi

Class Constraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.n_orm.storeapi.Constraint

  • public class Constraint
extends Object
    A restriction to a SimpleStore search. In case this restriction applies to a table (as in SimpleStore.get(String, Constraint, int, java.util.Set), returned rows should have key be between getStartKey() and getEndKey(). In case this restrictions applies to a column family (as in SimpleStore.get(String, String, String, Constraint), returned columns should have key be between getStartKey() and getEndKey().

        Describes a search for a particular key. To search for a range of a key of cardinality n, all values for k of cardinalities less than n must be supplied. startValue and endValue are both inclusive.
        Parameters:
        checkKeys - to check whether all keys with a lower category is given a value
